Product name: Vintage Soviet men's "East" ( "VOSTOK") automatic, Komandirskie watch , 21 jewels movement , great Vintage watch, new band. Amphibian!
Description:
Vintage men's Soviet wristwach "Komandirskie "  "EAST"- (" Vostok"). 21 jewels movement. Automatic! Amphibian!
This 1980's Vostok Komandirskie'  is a lovely civilian version of the Russian military watch. More information you can find here: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vostok_watches
The watch has been fully serviced,cleaned and oiled by a professional watch maker.The watch is working very accurately.
Vostok (Russian: Восток, meaning East*).The Vostok Company was founded in 1942 when one of the Moscow watch-making plants of the First Moscow Watch Factory was evacuated to Chistopol, a small town located on the Kama River in Tatarstan. Only defence equipment was produced during the war years, but as soon as the war was over the company started making mechanical wrist watches. However, the Company did not begin using the "Vostok" brand name until the 1960s. *Presumable "Vostok" brand was named after the Vostok space programme, which gave the initial advancement of the USSR in the Space race (as some others soviet watch brands, named to space topics in 1960s - Poljot and Raketa).

Product name: Vintage Wind Up Tin Race Car
Description:
With real estate it's "Location, Location, Location", right?  With toys, though, it's "Condition, Condition, Condition".  To that end here is one of two absolutely beautiful wind up tin cars that I recently acquired.  Take a good look at the pictures and you'll see a car that lead a very sheltered life.  How long a life that has been is somewhat of a mystery, so we're going to call it pre-1997.  Given its classic wind up mechanism, simple paint scheme and mid-60's open wheel race car style, it seems reasonable that it dates roughly from the Kennedy administration.  There are no maker marks or other distinguishable characteristics that would shed some light on who made this car, unfortunately.  If someone more knowledgeable than me sees this and wants to let me know, I would definitely appreciate it.  
The wind up mechanism functions as it should and the car will roll across the floor, though it's unlikely to set any land speed records in your living room.  I spent exactly zero seconds cleaning this car as I like things that are "barn fresh", and am banking on you, dear potential customer, feeling the same way.  A careful cleaning will no doubt reveal an even more attractive patina than what's visible in the photographs.
If you have any questions about anything I sell or care to discuss which George Harrison solo songs should have been Beatles recordings, feel free to drop me a line anytime.  As I rarely sleep, I'll get back to you surprisingly fast.  There are many more yard sale, junk store and estate sale items on their way so check back often as I attempt to sell you neat stuff.

Product name: RAINBOW BLAST Strobe LED Hula Hoop
Description:
This hoop will be handmade to order especially for YOU (with extra love, of course!)
--- PICKUP DISCOUNTS ---
Pick this hoop up from me in person and save up to 40% off the regular price! This offer is valid for orders picked up locally in Kansas City OR for orders picked up at music festivals! We will be vending Wakarusa, Electric Forest and Art Outside. We will be adding more events to this list so check out our events page for the most up to date calendar! View the events page here---  www.citivacreationz.com/vending-events/
All you need to do is purchase the 5 deposit listing and the rest will be due upon pick-up! View the deposit listings here ---  www.citivacreationz.com/reservations
--- CUSTOMER SERVICE & SATISFACTION GUARANTEE ---
We take pride in the fact that CitivaCreationz has one of the best reputations within the hoop community for providing amazing customer service to thousands of hoopers over the last five years. We are all hoopers here at CitivaCreationz, so we understand that this is a special purchase and we want to make sure that you are satisfied with your purchase. If you aren't happy with your CitivaCreationz LED hoop, you have one week from the delivery date to return it for a refund, no questions asked!
--- CONSCIOUSLY CRAFTED ---
Every step is taken to ensure that we leave the smallest carbon footprint possible when creating your hoops! Most of our materials are custom made and sourced locally, all packaging we receive with materials is reused, hoop boxes and shipping bags are made from recycled post consumer waste, shipping labels are printed on recycled paper, 100% of the unusable waste created is recycled (torn boxes, ends of tubing rolls, etc), and supplies are ordered in large quantities so that the delivery trucks have to make fewer trips to our shop! We are constantly finding new ways to improve reduce our impact on the environment, and by supporting us you too are supporting that movement!
--- WORRY-FREE WARRANTY ---
This hoop comes with a one year worry-free warranty which covers labor costs, burned out LEDs and wiring problems caused by a defect in construction. If your hoop ever needs to be repaired, just send it in and we will have it returned to you in a jiffy!
--- LED SEQUENCE ---
This hoop contains solid strobe LEDs sequenced in rainbow order around the hoop. Choose to have the hoop made with 18 LEDs, 27 LEDs or 36 LEDs. With the 18 LED and 27 LED option, there is NO battery gap (the 36 LED option is spaced closer together so there is a 1" battery gap/dark spot.)
--- TUBING ---
You can choose for this hoop to be made with either HDPE tubing or PolyPro tubing. With LED hoops, there is no noticeable difference in weight between the two types due to the extra weight of the components inside. We do not recommend one or the other, your decision should be made on what feels right to you...HDPE is more springy and PolyPro is more rigid. Keep in mind that PolyPro is more prone to cracking in colder temperatures, and is not available with 38" hoops.
--- LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN ---
Hoops in 3/4" tubing weigh about 12 ounces, and hoops in 5/8" tubing weigh about 8 ounces. The number of LEDs does not affect the weight. If you would like weight added to your hoop, just leave a note with your purchase and I will add extra weights for free!
--- COUNTER-BALANCED & RATTLE-FREE ---
Each hoop is counter-balanced for an even flow while hooping. The internal wires are also padded so that there is NO RATTLING during use, which ensures your hoop will have a long, happy life. 
--- COLLAPSIBLE ---
This hoop will collapse down to half its original size making it ideal for road trips, airplane travel, hiking excursions, bike rides and carrying around at festivals/events. You can take this hoop on any airline, and it is not counted as a carry-on! Protect your hoop and transport it easily with a custom handmade hoop bag ---  
https://www.etsy.com/listing/109482262
--- CONNECTION --- 
This hoop will turn on and off with a simple push button mechanism. This design is incredibly durable, and makes switching out batteries a cinch. Perfect for events where you don't have access to electricity! Choose between a standard 'outer' connection, or an upgraded 'inner' connection*. The inner connection has a smooth, sleek appearance and is slightly more balanced for the more advanced hooper. Please note that while the outer connector has an 'off' position, the inner connector does not (meaning you will have to remove the battery when you want to turn the hoop off.) Refer to photos for a comparison. *Inner connections are NOT available for 38" hoops!
--- BATTERY & CHARGER ---
Each hoop requires only one battery to turn on. You will receive one wall charger and one rechargeable lithium-ion battery with your order. Each battery takes about 2 hours to charge and will give you 1-2 hours of glow time on a full charge. Extra batteries are recommended so that you're never left in the dark! Be sure that you purchase the correct size of battery for your hoop - all 5/8" hoops will require the 'Featherweight (10440)" size and all 3/4" hoops will require the 'Normal (14500)" size. Batteries ship for free when purchased with an LED hoop. Purchase for 5 each here ---  
www.etsy.com/listing/76712206
--- SIZING OPTIONS ---
You may choose from a variety of even-numbered sizes between 26" and 38". If you would prefer an in-between size (31", 33", etc) be sure to include that in the NOTE TO SELLER box at checkout along with what size tubing you prefer! CitivaCreationz LED hoops are measured by outside diameter, meaning from outside edge to outside edge. Not sure which size you need? Here are some recommendations...
~38" OD (X-Large) : This size is great for beginner hoopers OR curvy body types OR tall body types (over 5'8") OR hoopers who prefer a slower hooping style. *Inner connection NOT available for 38" hoops!
~36" OD (Large) : This size is the most popular and recommended for anyone who doesn't fit into any of the other size descriptions. Great for intermediate hoopers and children under 12.
~34" OD (Medium) : This size is the second most popular and is perfect for those of you who have a smaller body frame, or prefer a faster style of hooping with intermediate/advanced skills.
~32" OD (Small) : This size is primarily for hoopers who prefer off-body and advanced tricks, or who have a very small body type.
~30" OD (X-Small) or 28" OD (XX-Small): This size is for advanced and/or off-body hoopers. Also a great size for doubles. Not recommended for anyone who hasn't used this size hoop before!
--- GRIP OPTIONS ---

Product name: 5m of Goldschild Linen Thread, non-waxed, 3-ply
Description:
This listing is for 5m of Goldschild's Linethread, NeL 18/3 linen (sold in the USA as Londonderry thread). It is made from the longest and most valuable line fibres of the flax plant.
This thread is good for a broad variety of textile works, most noteworthy embroidery, lace making, and crocheting. It is dyed using traditional techniques which give beautiful, natural looking results which are light and water resistant.
NeL 18/3 is one of the standard thicknesses for bookbinding, however, this thread is softer and not as tightly twisted as bookbinding thread usually is. It is an interesting addition to a bookbinder's repertoire of thread nonetheless. It can be used for binding light and small books (like one signature pamphlets), for Asian stab bindings, or for decorative stitches including headbands and embroidery on covers.
Satisfied customers have also used it for crocheting interesting jewellery like accessories, embroidery on leather and used it as a colourful string for packing merchandise. 
Generally the colors survive washing at 60°, but the thread might shrink. Pull in shape and dry under tension to prevent embroidered fabrics from warping and distorting.
PLEASE NOTE:
-----------------------
Colours viewed on a screen look different than the real thing, the photos in this listing are only for reference.
Furthermore the exact color varies from dye lot to dye lot. Therefore thread bought under the same name at different times may look different. Better order enough thread to last through your whole project.
